item.title: Our First Month Back In Montroy
item.description: Only here a few days barely settled in and it Flo’s Birthday 59yrs. Went to the local Pizza place to celebrate Flo’s big day and Amanda and Charlott joined us and supplied the Birthday Cake. The food was VG as always. .
